# clAIre 🤖
## Autonomous AI Assistive Robot for Elderly & Disabled Individuals

> Submitted to Samsung Solve for Tomorrow 2026

---

# Overview

clAIre is an autonomous assistive robot designed to improve safety, independence, and quality of life for elderly and disabled individuals.

The system combines:
- Artificial Intelligence
- Computer Vision
- Autonomous Navigation
- Voice Interaction
- Emergency Response Technology
- Real-Time Obstacle Detection

clAIre was developed to address critical community challenges including:
- Falls among seniors
- Delayed emergency response
- Isolation and loneliness
- Limited mobility
- Accessibility barriers

By integrating robotics and AI into a single assistive platform, clAIre acts as a smart mobility companion capable of following users, detecting hazards, providing reminders, and assisting during emergencies.

---

# Community Problem

In Lake County, many seniors live independently and face growing health and safety challenges. Falls, mobility limitations, and delayed access to help can quickly become dangerous emergencies.

Many existing solutions are:
- Expensive
- Difficult to use
- Limited to one specific function
- Not accessible for elderly users

clAIre was created to provide an affordable, intelligent, and user-friendly solution that improves everyday safety and independence.

---

# Key Features

## 🚨 Real-Time Obstacle Detection
- Detects walls, furniture, stairs, and moving obstacles
- Provides verbal safety warnings
- Stops automatically when hazards are detected

## 🧭 Autonomous Following System
- Tracks and follows the user automatically
- Maintains safe following distance
- Reduces physical effort for users

## 🗣️ AI Voice Assistant
- Hands-free voice interaction
- Natural voice commands
- Spoken feedback and confirmations

## 📞 Emergency Calling System
- Voice-activated emergency response
- Can contact caregivers or emergency services
- Provides rapid assistance during emergencies

## 💊 Medication & Reminder Support
- Health reminders
- Daily schedule assistance
- Voice-based notifications

## 📱 Smart Companion App
- Displays robot status
- Health reminders
- Battery monitoring
- Alerts and notifications
- Logged activity tracking

