# System Architecture

clAIre consists of four major subsystems:

## 1. Display & Interaction Module

### Components
- Raspberry Pi
- Hamtysan Monitor
- Speakers
- Microphone

### Functions
- Voice processing
- Audio responses
- System coordination
- User interaction
- Emergency communication

---

## 2. Navigation & Vision Module

### Components
- High-resolution camera
- ESP32 vision processor

### Functions
- Real-time obstacle detection
- User tracking
- Environmental monitoring
- Safe path calculation
- Autonomous navigation

---

## 3. Motor Control System

### Components
- 550 35T brushed motor
- 370 planetary motors
- ESC motor controllers
- PCB motor driver board

### Functions
- Smooth movement
- Precise turning
- Speed control
- Emergency stopping

---

## 4. Power System

### Components
- Dual 5200mAh lithium-ion batteries
- Crawler BDC80 controllers

### Features
- 8–12 hour battery life
- Redundant power architecture
- Battery protection systems

